  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[PET TOWN]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> An MR Simulation with Your Own Pet!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/f4125ce4b3b9a60b3ead41e8809f9988.avif?t=1732528013\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Game Introduction</strong>]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PET TOWN is a casual simulation game that offers a unique experience, allowing you to cross between virtual and real worlds with your adorable pets. Switch seamlessly between VR and MR modes as you care for, play with, and bond with your pets. More than just a simulation, PetTown offers a heartfelt connection with your pets, bringing warmth and joy through genuine interaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Intuitive Hand Gesture Controls]</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the UI using only your 'left hand'! Thumbs up to open the menu, thumbs down to close it. Show your palm to reveal the game exit UI.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/61a538bd43bbc1b5c2f59a8e1b2a6759.poster.avif?t=1732528013\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/61a538bd43bbc1b5c2f59a8e1b2a6759.webm?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/61a538bd43bbc1b5c2f59a8e1b2a6759.mp4?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Hybrid Mode: Switch Between VR and MR Freely]</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transition to MR mode with a scissors-hand gesture, and return to VR by clenching your fist. In MR mode, bond with your pets in your real-world space, while VR mode immerses you in a virtual environment to share time with your pets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/2bd3e5cf44bf0cd09d72a1a4c335497f.poster.avif?t=1732528013\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/2bd3e5cf44bf0cd09d72a1a4c335497f.webm?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/2bd3e5cf44bf0cd09d72a1a4c335497f.mp4?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Relationship]</strong>:<strong> Realistic Pet Interactions </strong> Touch and pet your pets to engage with them, and observe their expressive emotional responses. Their actions and facial expressions are as lifelike as in the real world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/464980c68381fb93599ebe31fe250200.avif?t=1732528013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras_big/464980c68381fb93599ebe31fe250200.avif?t=1732528013 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Care]: Play with Your Pet! </strong> Play fetch, feed, and bathe your pets to strengthen your bond and make them happy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/6c84efa2a90aacf259df7b09a26a0375.avif?t=1732528013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras_big/6c84efa2a90aacf259df7b09a26a0375.avif?t=1732528013 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Round]: Fun Mini-Games </strong> Enjoy a variety of mini-games, such as hurdle jumping and obstacle dodging, to have fun with your pets. These games provide opportunities for you to get even closer to your pets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/2ca4e7fee596748119d6bfd53af9ac94.avif?t=1732528013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras_big/2ca4e7fee596748119d6bfd53af9ac94.avif?t=1732528013 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Shop]: Customize Your Pet </strong> Buy outfits and accessories for your pet from the shop to give them a unique style, also purchase food to feed your hungry pet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/ad3ba434e02f03541a46fbc4aeca6166.avif?t=1732528013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras_big/ad3ba434e02f03541a46fbc4aeca6166.avif?t=1732528013 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Create special moments with your pets in PET TOWN. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>An adventure that crosses between the real and virtual world is waiting for you!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[PET TOWN]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> An MR Simulation with Your Own Pet!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/f4125ce4b3b9a60b3ead41e8809f9988.avif?t=1732528013\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Game Introduction</strong>]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PET TOWN is a casual simulation game that offers a unique experience, allowing you to cross between virtual and real worlds with your adorable pets. Switch seamlessly between VR and MR modes as you care for, play with, and bond with your pets. More than just a simulation, PetTown offers a heartfelt connection with your pets, bringing warmth and joy through genuine interaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Intuitive Hand Gesture Controls]</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with the UI using only your 'left hand'! Thumbs up to open the menu, thumbs down to close it. Show your palm to reveal the game exit UI.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/61a538bd43bbc1b5c2f59a8e1b2a6759.poster.avif?t=1732528013\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/61a538bd43bbc1b5c2f59a8e1b2a6759.webm?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/61a538bd43bbc1b5c2f59a8e1b2a6759.mp4?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Hybrid Mode: Switch Between VR and MR Freely]</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transition to MR mode with a scissors-hand gesture, and return to VR by clenching your fist. In MR mode, bond with your pets in your real-world space, while VR mode immerses you in a virtual environment to share time with your pets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/2bd3e5cf44bf0cd09d72a1a4c335497f.poster.avif?t=1732528013\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/2bd3e5cf44bf0cd09d72a1a4c335497f.webm?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/2bd3e5cf44bf0cd09d72a1a4c335497f.mp4?t=1732528013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Relationship]</strong>:<strong> Realistic Pet Interactions </strong> Touch and pet your pets to engage with them, and observe their expressive emotional responses. Their actions and facial expressions are as lifelike as in the real world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras/464980c68381fb93599ebe31fe250200.avif?t=1732528013\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298840/extras_big/464980c68381fb93599ebe31fe250200.avif?t=1732528013 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[Care]: Play with Your Pet! </strong> Play fetch, feed, and bathe your pets to strengthen your bond and make them happy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste